poolcounter-desc:
{{desc|name=Pool Counter|url=https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:PoolCounter}}
A pool counter keeps track of the running processes on a cluster of processors, and may or may not grant a job access to the processing pool.

'''Note''': the word "counter" relates to the [[:w:en:Counter_(furniture)|counter in a shop, bank, or hotel]], not to the verb "to count".
